<L>__{exterior street night}
<A>__{leopold walks out of the restaurant trying to remain calm. his emotions get the best of him. finally, exhausted, he winds up walking along central park south. hansom carriages wait to be taken out. he approaches slowly. he stops along side one of the cabs and strokes the horse's head. he looks at the horse for a long time. then he looks at the skyscrapers surrounding him, deciding what to do. he lays his face against the horse's head, torn.}
